played by the rules from the beginning in the selection process for 
that new airport coats said 
he is trying to block 52 million the city requested from the 
federal aviation administration to produce a master plan for the 
airport 
rep pete visclosky dind has accused us transportation 
secretary samuel skinner former chairman of the regional 
transportation authority of northern illinois of favoring the city 
all ive agreed to do is not eliminate any choices skinner 
said last week after meeting with coats and dole 
