president bush back from summit talks where 
he pledged a global partnership with japan now faces the 
challenge of proving he can act on his vow to turn around the us 
trade deficit with japan 
even as the president headed back sunday from the meeting with 
japanese prime minister toshiki kaifu in rancho mirage calif 
