falcon say they are eager to return 
were here not because we want to be but because of the 
repression she said i couldnt see any use to continue 
battling a political asylum claim that didnt have any validity 
the ins rules on political asylum in large part are based on 
state department advisory opinions for each case most denials 
occur because analysts rule applicants are economic rather than 
political refugees 
