the looting 
ciskei a 3600squaremile territory of about 1 million people 
is not recognized as sovereign by any country other than south 
africa 
south africa has made it and three other homelands independent 
as part of efforts to create separate homelands for blacks but no 
other nations recognize them as independent residents in the 
homelands lose south african citizenship but the pretoria 
government pumps millions of dollars into the homelands to keep 
them afloat 
