major advertising campaign 
many viewers have watched their evening news on the same network 
for a generation amos said adding a 25yearold ingrained 
habit thats a tough habit to break 
its going to take a long time to make the public aware that 
we are here he said less than 60 percent of the nations 
households have cable or access to the program 
 
