its a posse of volunteers ready to gallop off 
after horse thieves and it keeps a noose handy the wild west no 
upstate new york circa 1990 admittedly the horse thief trackers 
of the empire state havent had much to do most of this century 
but they stay organized in case theyre ever called on 
