<TEXT>
the 167th annual meeting of the 
schodack stuyvesant kinderhook and chatham society for the 
detection of horse thieves is hereby called to order any old 
business 
not since that horse was stolen 73 years ago 
new business 
not till the next horse is stolen 
whats on the menu this year 
same as always mincedham sandwiches clam chowder and oyster 
stew 
meetings adjourned lets put on the feed bags 
thats as lively as it gets these days for the horse thief 
trackers of columbia county 30 miles south of albany the group 
