trail dogs the horse in folklore and archaeological evidence of 
eohippus the prehistoric forerunner of todays horse 
even so the posses of columbia and dutchess counties wont be 
saddling up anytime soon 
with the state of modern law enforcement klose said we 
dont take things into our own hands anymore 
