securities industry robinson said 
in the same statement clark said this vote of confidence from 
american express gives us the support we will need to implement the 
findings of our strategic review and achieve successful performance 
levels as a leader in the securities industry 
shearson has been searching for capital to avoid a threatened 
downgrading of its credit rating which could increase its costs by 
forcing it to pay higher interest rates on its borrowings 
at the same time american express had been seeking to reduce 
its 61 percent stake in shearson to less than half to remove the 
firm from its balance sheet and reduce its exposure to wall 
streets sharp profit swings a sharp drop in shearsons share 
