jointly gyllenhammar said we will find costcutting earlier 
but not of any dramatic nature 
the two automakers announced feb 23 an agreement in which they 
will take stakes in each other and work jointly in the future in 
such areas as research product development and purchasing 
the accord aims to achieve economies of scale and to extend the 
reach of both companies although each will remain legally 
independent executives at both companies say the volvo and renault 
brand names will remain distinct 
