coffee futures prices soared above 1 a pound monday on new 
yorks coffee sugar amp cocoa exchange amid rising concern about 
tight availability of highquality coffee 
on other futures markets copper futures surged cotton futures 
were up sharply energy futures were higher precious metals were 
mixed grains and soybeans were mixed and livestock andmeat 
futures were mixed 
