consecutive day of unusual strength was not related to any change 
in the supplydemand picture but to the same factors that have 
recently supported the market 
those factors include civil strife in the ivory coast a coffee 
supply shortfall in mexico a lack of availability from ecuador and 
poor growing conditions for coffee in colombia 
