the board of directors of general motors corp 
approved an antigreenmail policy prompting a stockholder to 
withdraw her proposal against such payoffs 
the policy approved monday prohibits the purchase of shares at 
an abovemarket price from anyone owning more than 3 percent of the 
voting power of the corporations stock the policy applies only if 
the stockholder has held his or her shares for less than two years 
